genresAdvancedInfo.name: kids dance party
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Kids dance party music is designed to get children up and moving. It features catchy tunes, simple lyrics, and upbeat rhythms that encourage kids to dance and have fun. The music often incorporates popular children's characters and themes, making it easy for kids to relate to and enjoy. It is a great way to get kids active and engaged in music and dance.
